In the Instagram video, Mbuso Mandela is heard admitting to abusing women and strangling his girlfriend. Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A video of Nelson Mandela's grandson admitting to abusing his girlfriend has gone viral on social media. In the Instagram video, Mbuso Mandela is heard admitting to abusing women and strangling his girlfriend. He goes on to say the video is his way of confessing to the abuse. READ:Â Police union: Report paints gloomy picture of fight against domestic abuse In a bizarre twist, a woman claiming to be the girlfriend posted a video alleging the abuse never took place. In it she says Mandela posted the video after she called his bluff. This is not the first time Mandela has been linked to a scandal. In 2015 he appeared in court for allegedly raping a 15-year-old girl. That case was later withdrawn.